#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:2
#: c87710a6805d4756aaaa01fc3a97adf6
msgid "安信可 LoRa/LoRaWan系列模块 FAQ"
msgstr "Ai-Thinker LoRa/LoRaWAN Series Module FAQ"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:17
#: 51e836cca5404227acccf0dc2d66328d
msgid "Ra-01模块和Ra-02模块的区别是什么？"
msgstr "What is the difference between the Ra-01 module and the Ra-02 module?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:18
#: 78928f1a0f434dd7a582f5481b57ebfe
msgid ""
"答：Ra-01，Ra-02内部只有一个SX1278芯片，两者的区别就是一个天线座子（Ra-02多了"
"一个Ipex座子）"
msgstr ""
"A: Both Ra-01 and Ra-02 have only one SX1278 chip inside. The difference is "
"the antenna connector. Ra-02 has an additional IPEX connector."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:21
#: cd9dafc508f24f72b8ab4f0e05c5fb1e
msgid ""
"RHF78-052模块用OTAA入网模式失败了，显示join failed 有什么办法去定位失败原因"
"吗?"
msgstr ""
"The RHF78-052 module failed to join the network in OTAA mode and shows "
"\"join failed\". Is there any way to locate the cause of the failure?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:22
#: 196b100230c9495ea0a5790d8d96ac02
msgid "AT+CH=CN470 设置为该地区信道"
msgstr "Set the channel for this region with AT+CH=CN470."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:25
#: 605542946ff041ffbd49418591bfb07e
msgid ""
"SX1278有寻址或数据加密功能吗?是不是别人的1278只要与我同频就可以收到所有数据?"
msgstr ""
"Does SX1278 support addressing or data encryption? If another SX1278 is on "
"the same frequency as mine, can it receive all my data?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:26
#: e8f1618699314d74aa142e298e394f10
msgid "答：没有寻址加密，同频都可以收到。"
msgstr ""
"A: It does not support addressing or encryption. Devices on the same "
"frequency can receive the data."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:29
#: 8d8522fb64f24c37a7bf54dc85e4acaa
msgid "LoRa模块如何进入低功耗模式（睡眠模式），低功耗模式下功耗是多少？"
msgstr ""
"How can a LoRa module enter low-power mode (sleep mode)? What is the power "
"consumption in low-power mode?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:30
#: eeddc94ce45845ca955c03f859199d56
msgid ""
"通过SPI通信写寄存器的方式进入低功耗模式，低功耗模式下电流为0.2uA（微安"
"μA）------注：此方法不适用Ra-06"
msgstr ""
"Enter low-power mode by writing registers through SPI communication. The "
"current in low-power mode is 0.2uA.  ------Note: This method does not apply "
"to Ra-06."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:33
#: 5f279df49d26423ca5dac12dd490d316
msgid "LoRa模块上使用的是普通晶体还是TCXO石英晶体，频点为多少？"
msgstr ""
"Does the LoRa module use a normal crystal or a TCXO crystal? What is the "
"frequency?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:34
#: e2e95e9dd7ad45e892a86d997b0cb317
msgid "答：使用的是普通晶体，频点为32Mhz"
msgstr "A: It uses a normal crystal with a frequency of 32MHz."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:37
#: 49b17d297d5f45b18f1cb8c8201ed425
msgid "关于SX1278射频模式切换的引脚要如何设置？"
msgstr "How should the pins for SX1278 RF mode switching be configured?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:38
#: ead6c1e7b30e483aa8e8af6ad64c0f8c
msgid ""
"答：LoRa模组没有射频开关芯片，不支持这样切换，直接通过SPI配置寄存器就可以使用"
"LoRa模组"
msgstr ""
"A: The LoRa module does not have an RF switch chip and does not support this "
"type of switching. You can use the LoRa module directly by configuring "
"registers through SPI."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:41
#: cfe5fbf6f6974e50b74d91cabdb23abd
msgid ""
"不同的LoRa模块之间通信，可以给LoRa模块加地址吗，用来区分是哪一个LoRa模块?"
msgstr ""
"Can LoRa modules communicate with each other? Can an address be added to "
"distinguish which LoRa module it is?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:42
#: f843b1ac96cb48878a02ad4012dcd746
msgid "答：可以，在有效负载的前两个字节定义为地址"
msgstr ""
"A: Yes. You can define the first two bytes of the payload as the address."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:45
#: 4909f16a3b984a5f825f1276fde3272e
msgid "信号带宽（BW），符号速率（Rs）和数据速率（DR）间的关系是什么？"
msgstr ""
"What is the relationship between signal bandwidth (BW), symbol rate (Rs), "
"and data rate (DR)?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:46
#: 4fcebebdb4da49169e1e5a319188ac52
msgid ""
"Rs=BW/(2^SF)、DR= SF*( BW/2^SF)*CR，但我们建议你使用Semtech LoRa调制解调器计"
"算器按照不同的配置选型评估数据速率和传输时间。"
msgstr ""
"Rs = BW / (2^SF), DR = SF * (BW / 2^SF) * CR. However, we recommend using "
"the Semtech LoRa Modem Calculator to evaluate the data rate and transmission "
"time according to different configurations."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:49
#: 2227f02bc3e84947818311f981517b80
msgid "LoRa设备天线上可以达到的实际Tx功率是多少？"
msgstr ""
"What is the actual Tx power that can be achieved at the antenna of a LoRa "
"device?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:50
#: 2882e9aee96b4914a276241ff64e4724
msgid ""
"在芯片引脚输出的功率是+20dBm，经过匹配/滤波损耗后在天线后，在天线上功  率是"
"+19dBm +/-0.5dB。最大输出功率在不同的地区有不同的规定，LoRaWAN规范定义了不同"
"地区不同的输出功率使链路预算最大化。"
msgstr ""
"The output power at the chip pin is +20dBm. After matching/filtering loss, "
"the power at the antenna is +19dBm +/-0.5dB. The maximum output power is "
"regulated differently in different regions. The LoRaWAN specification "
"defines different output powers for different regions to maximize the link "
"budget."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:53
#: a4f5bde05b5b47b4b492f0cd9e2cc902
msgid "当两个LoRa模块不能相互通信时，故障检测的步骤是什么？"
msgstr ""
"What are the troubleshooting steps when two LoRa modules cannot communicate "
"with each other?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:54
#: aded8fb793634a4eb0ed6dc5c73fe0ee
msgid ""
"答：首先，在两个设备间检查由晶振引起的频率偏移。带宽（BW）、中心频率和数据速"
"率这些都源自晶振频率。其次，检查在两边的软件/固件设置，确保频率、带宽、扩频因"
"子、编码率和数据包结构是一致的。"
msgstr ""
"A: First, check the frequency offset caused by the crystal oscillator "
"between the two devices. Bandwidth (BW), center frequency, and data rate are "
"all derived from the crystal frequency. Second, check the software/firmware "
"settings on both sides to ensure that the frequency, bandwidth, spreading "
"factor, coding rate, and packet structure are consistent."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:57
#: 8c92f675dba34f52ae5ad2c5e03714c4
msgid "LoRa模块可以发送或者接受一个无限长度的有效载荷数据包吗？"
msgstr ""
"Can a LoRa module send or receive a payload packet of unlimited length?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:58
#: 905af7f547394741b3db4c9c9404ddf7
msgid "答：不可以，在LoRa发送或者接受中最大数据包长度是256个字节"
msgstr ""
"A: No. In LoRa transmission or reception, the maximum packet length is 256 "
"bytes."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:61
#: 3b633a31e39542a498bc410158de23bc
msgid "LoRa模式的有效载荷长度可以用任意数据配置为256个字节吗？"
msgstr ""
"Can the payload length in LoRa mode be configured to 256 bytes with "
"arbitrary data?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:62
#: d143c01f0b10417baa8c6ec315507812
msgid ""
"答：SX127x LoRa设备在LoRa模式中有一个256字节的FIFO。理论上，所有的256"
"字                 节都可以用于TX或RX。然而，用低数据速率配置，256字节有效载"
"荷的传输时          间将会很长（几秒或更长），这对于抗衰落和高干扰环境是不好"
"的。在大多数环境             中这不是一个健壮的配置，因此建议如果想要一个使用"
"低数据速率长的有效载荷，            那么数据包可以分成几个短的数据包。"
msgstr ""
"A: SX127x LoRa devices have a 256-byte FIFO in LoRa mode. In theory, all 256 "
"bytes can be used for TX or RX. However, with a low data rate configuration, "
"the transmission time for a 256-byte payload will be very long, several "
"seconds or more, which is not good for anti-fading and high-interference "
"environments. In most environments this is not a robust configuration. "
"Therefore, if a long payload is required at a low data rate, it is "
"recommended to split the packet into several shorter packets."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:65
#: ff39a9c35e684a93b67ffeef80cb7b26
msgid "LoRa网关的容量是多少？一个网关可以连接多少个节点？"
msgstr ""
"What is the capacity of a LoRa gateway? How many nodes can one gateway "
"connect to?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:66
#: 15d4d5cfadaa4042bd151f33c4ae8852
msgid ""
"答：首先最重要的是，容量是在一定时间内节接受数据包数量的一个结果。一个"
"SX1301       有8个通道，使用LoRaWAN协议每天可以接受接近150万包数据。因此，如"
"果你的应用每小时发送一个包，那么一个SX1301网关可以处理大约62500个终端设备。"
msgstr ""
"A: Most importantly, capacity is determined by the number of packets "
"received within a certain period of time. An SX1301 has 8 channels and can "
"receive nearly 1.5 million packets per day using the LoRaWAN protocol. "
"Therefore, if your application sends one packet per hour, one SX1301 gateway "
"can handle about 62,500 end devices."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:69
#: aae4480d55ec485196768a675595b1b3
msgid "如果不能达到+20dBm，如何解决输出功率问题？"
msgstr ""
"If +20dBm cannot be achieved, how should the output power issue be resolved?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:70
#: a34ae27f749f416e8e18d4a13dd73e96
msgid ""
"答：1.请确认你连接到正确的引脚（PA_Boost）设置，20dBm输出的引脚。每个频段有两"
"个输出端口。一个是高功率端口称为PA_boost，另一个是高效端口称为RFO。"
msgstr ""
"A: 1. Confirm that you are connected to the correct pin, PA_Boost, for 20dBm "
"output. Each frequency band has two output ports. One is the high-power port "
"called PA_Boost, and the other is the high-efficiency port called RFO."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:71
#: 14878f8ad3254577849622d7c2f23fb1
msgid ""
"2. 然后，检测软件配置。应该正确地配置好三个寄存器：RegPaConfig、RegOcp 和 "
"RegPaDac。这意味着你在软件中应选择正确的引脚做相应的输出，再依据你需要的功耗"
"级别设置正确的值 3. 确认他们与Semtech参考设计相一致以便设计一个好的PCB布局。"
"这对于可能达到最大的输出功率来说是重要的。"
msgstr ""
"2. Then check the software configuration. Three registers should be "
"configured correctly: RegPaConfig, RegOcp, and RegPaDac. This means that the "
"correct pin should be selected in the software for the corresponding output, "
"and the correct values should be set according to the required power "
"consumption level. 3. Confirm that the design is consistent with the Semtech "
"reference design in order to achieve a good PCB layout. This is important "
"for reaching the maximum possible output power."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:75
#: b1406aabd1ea42e6b27839065a91d580
msgid "LoRa通信距离和什么有关？"
msgstr "What factors affect LoRa communication distance?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:76
#: 7518facb95f949218ed1232d65b4e190
msgid ""
"1，发射功率。 2，天线角度，通常天线应该相互平行。 3，天线的中心频率是否与模块"
"通讯频率匹配。每个天线都有一定的频率范围，称为带宽，在这个范围内，天线阻抗最"
"小，效率最高，这个范围的中间最佳点即中心频率，驻波比最小。 4，LoRa的配置参"
"数。空中速率越高，LoRa发送数据的速率越快，但是接收灵敏度就降低了。所以要提高"
"通讯距离，就需要适当降低空中速率。空中速率大小和扩频因子SF、带宽BW、编码率有"
"关。空中速率与扩频因子、编码率大小反相关，与带宽正相关。例如，远距离测试时，"
"参数可以这样设置：扩频因子:12；带宽BW:6；编码率:2，注意在低速率通讯时，开启"
"LoRa低速率优化功能。 5，程序错误。典型的是PA设置错误，LoRa 1278/1276有三个射"
"频信号发送口，分别是RFO_LF: 低频率发送口，效率高；PA_BOOST: 20dBm信号放大口，"
"安信可的Ra01,Ra02使用的是该发送口，程序里务必开启；RFO_HF: 高频率发送口，效率"
"高 根据硬件原理图连接，选择相应的发送口。"
msgstr ""
"1. Transmit power. 2. Antenna angle. Usually the antennas should be parallel "
"to each other. 3. Whether the center frequency of the antenna matches the "
"communication frequency of the module. Each antenna has a certain frequency "
"range, called bandwidth. Within this range, the antenna impedance is the "
"lowest and the efficiency is the highest. The best point in the middle of "
"this range is the center frequency, where the standing wave ratio is the "
"lowest. 4. LoRa configuration parameters. The higher the air data rate, the "
"faster LoRa sends data, but the receiving sensitivity decreases. Therefore, "
"to increase communication distance, the air data rate should be reduced "
"appropriately. The air data rate is related to spreading factor SF, "
"bandwidth BW, and coding rate. The air data rate is negatively correlated "
"with the spreading factor and coding rate, and positively correlated with "
"bandwidth. For example, for long-distance testing, the parameters can be set "
"as follows: spreading factor: 12; bandwidth BW: 6; coding rate: 2. Note that "
"when communicating at a low data rate, the LoRa low data rate optimization "
"function should be enabled. 5. Program errors. A typical issue is incorrect "
"PA configuration. LoRa 1278/1276 has three RF signal transmission ports: "
"RFO_LF, a low-frequency transmission port with high efficiency; PA_BOOST, a "
"20 dBm signal amplification port, which is used by Ai-Thinker Ra-01 and "
"Ra-02 and must be enabled in the program; and RFO_HF, a high-frequency "
"transmission port with high efficiency. Select the corresponding "
"transmission port according to the hardware schematic connection."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:84
#: 9e60e59128b849f98c2496fc3fa3bc3d
msgid "Ra-01这个可以用线连单片机吗？"
