msgstr "What is the approximate gain of Ra-01 and Ra-02?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:109
#: 76e58262dd2142f6b7e6e8f5129c1caf
msgid "1.5db"
msgstr "1.5dB."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:112
#: 95e38c734a22408d964dc35be2fe3841
msgid "Ra-01模组上的晶振是多少频率的？需要这个参数"
msgstr ""
"What is the frequency of the crystal on the Ra-01 module? This parameter is "
