#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:120
#: b2cb9cf26a0146ccac22b6cd59bbc6f5
msgid "Ra-06可以和LoRa网关配合吗 ？RHF76-052可以吗 ？Ra06只能点对点传输"
msgstr ""
