msgid ""
"IO2引脚和IO11引脚，IO2为烧录引脚，正常使用需要保持低电平或者悬空，IO11引脚为"
"系统引脚，正常使用必须为高电平或者悬空"
msgstr ""
"IO2 and IO11. IO2 is the programming pin and should be kept low or floating "
"during normal use. IO11 is a system pin and must be high or floating during "
"normal use."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:996
#: 5bad32cd4208482ab99790a83a816d0f
msgid "Ra-01S中的DIO1不使用中断触发的形式，可以修改代码实现收发模式切换吗"
msgstr ""
"If DIO1 on Ra-01S is not used as an interrupt trigger, can the code be "
"modified to implement transmit/receive mode switching?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:997
#: c79efafc7ae44fffbeeb08c7473a83a5
msgid "可以通过修改代码实现，但是需对寄存器手册比较熟悉"
msgstr ""
"Yes, it can be implemented by modifying the code, but you need to be "
"familiar with the register manual."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1000
#: 4dc9c38352854b7dbb3b36ce9469b0da
msgid "LoRa测试底板能焊接哪些模组，使用上有什么需要注意的"
msgstr ""
"Which modules can be soldered onto the LoRa test baseboard, and what should "
"be noted during use?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1001
#: 25fa3793c4c84cc0b61bd769bd62266f
msgid ""
"测试底板能焊接Ra-01/02/01S/01SC等模组，其中，Ra-01/02在STM32例程上需要接DIO0"
"引脚，Ra-01S/SC需要接DIO1和BUSY引脚"
msgstr ""
"The test baseboard can be soldered with Ra-01/02/01S/01SC and other modules. "
"When using the STM32 example, Ra-01/02 need to connect the DIO0 pin, while "
"Ra-01S/SC need to connect DIO1 and BUSY pins."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1004
#: aab39ff49a7047859f5f9866e42e8b31
msgid ""
"Ra-08开发板的Class B入网方式，重启的情况下数据无法传输到服务器，显示计数不"
"对，是为何？"
msgstr ""
"For Ra-08 development board Class B join mode, why cannot data be "
"transmitted to the server after restart, and why does it show a counter "
"mismatch?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1005
#: f2c6aca44f154e349ba91973219e73db
msgid ""
"Class B入网方式不需要做入网动作，因此重启的情况下，计数将重置为0，而服务器的"
"计数值不变，因此，一旦计数值对不上，服务器将丢弃该数据。"
msgstr ""
"Class B join mode does not require a join operation. Therefore, after "
"restart, the counter is reset to 0, while the server counter remains "
"unchanged. Once the counters do not match, the server discards the data."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1008
#: 180455c268904f41a4dbd8847d919233
msgid "Ra-02模组的ipex接口是什么规格的？"
msgstr "What specification is the IPEX interface on the Ra-02 module?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1009
#: 0b679a5b0c4943e5a2b987e9b64db05b
msgid "我司所有带IPEX底座的模组均是搭配的IPEX 1代底座。"
msgstr ""
"All modules from our company with IPEX sockets use IPEX generation 1 sockets."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1012
#: 53f1afbe2bf44f5b9b43b3665cfb49ff
msgid ""
"Ra-02模组我不小心用螺丝刀碰一下就没信号了，但是如果MCU重启又有信号了，是什么"
"原因呢？"
msgstr ""
"I accidentally touched the Ra-02 module with a screwdriver and it lost "
"signal, but the signal returns after MCU restart. What is the reason?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1013
#: 99f7b49401c44ac68e672efdb30b1b3a
msgid "天线短路了，需分离之后重置射频发射或者接收功能。"
msgstr ""
"The antenna was short-circuited. It needs to be separated and then the RF "
"transmit or receive function should be reset."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1016
#: fbfaf5932ac042d497042b622c31a660
msgid "Ra-08中的SPI引脚是否就是规格书中标注的SSP引脚？"
msgstr "Are the SPI pins on Ra-08 the SSP pins marked in the specification?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1017
#: 73c0f929be754e59a59aeb592adab176
msgid "是的。"
msgstr "Yes."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1020
#: 6958be3e27d5491caf8b82515c0b19db
msgid ""
"Ra-01模块内置的SX1278芯片，在初始化配置时PA输出引脚应当设置为RFO还是PA_BOOST"
msgstr ""
"For the SX1278 chip built into the Ra-01 module, should the PA output pin be "
"configured as RFO or PA_BOOST during initialization?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1021
#: 7eef08a161bc466db72bb1620f3951b9
msgid "设置PA_BOOST"
msgstr "Set it to PA_BOOST."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1024
#: 4a4d5bb12f554c9f85bd24b8fba010a2
msgid "Ra-01S模块内部芯片外部有没有加PA放大器"
msgstr ""
"Does the Ra-01S module have an external PA amplifier added outside the "
"internal chip?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1025
#: 207c3186c25c4afe8aef0d186fa6b53e
msgid "没有添加放大器"
msgstr "No amplifier is added."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1028
#: 48d3ae8106864ddca7624e6726f4833c
msgid "LoRa模块能否用在水表上"
msgstr "Can LoRa modules be used in water meters?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1032
#: c1d32a177e6f43cf99be1894ba68cf92
msgid "有没有不限包长度的lora模组"
msgstr "Are there any LoRa modules with unlimited packet length?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1033
#: 2b378e9acc2943589b9099264c212ea9
msgid "目前lora模块最大包长度为250个字节，没有不限包长度的"
msgstr ""
"Currently, the maximum packet length of LoRa modules is 250 bytes. There is "
"no module with unlimited packet length."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1036
#: da48a59b849f4d3fb7bf64f717c55fbf
msgid "请问Ra-08模组支持设置扩频因子么？"
msgstr "Does the Ra-08 module support setting the spreading factor?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1037
#: 1f5f12e168f747d6b3537dca19724505
msgid "支持通过AT指令设置扩频因子，在设置之前实现关闭ADR功能；"
msgstr ""
"Yes. The spreading factor can be set through AT commands. ADR must be "
"disabled before setting it."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1040
#: 4ccb0e2f2a504ab6944b536926c4b051
msgid "Ra-08模块能否当网关使用"
msgstr "Can the Ra-08 module be used as a gateway?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1041
#: 69c8555f968445e3a703d5312deded1d
msgid "不能，只能当节点"
msgstr "No. It can only be used as a node."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1044
#: aff960cc9c3d448f8553140d19f9d094
msgid "RG-02支持连接helium平台吗"
msgstr "Does RG-02 support connection to the Helium platform?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1048
#: 8fb08c8153a44745a5894e185161c4f0
msgid "LoRa模块的信号能穿透铁皮盒子吗"
msgstr "Can the signal of a LoRa module penetrate an iron box?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1049
#: aca5b3dac1a44714bfd1664ff639b4b1
msgid "不能穿透，信号会被铁皮盒子吸收"
msgstr ""
"No. The signal cannot penetrate it; it will be absorbed by the iron box."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1052
#: f95f8401fd7743d28a858561bdbab0df
msgid "Ra-01SC模块如果不使用IPEX座子，可以直接焊接天线引脚引天线出来吗"
msgstr ""
"If the Ra-01SC module does not use the IPEX connector, can the antenna pin "
"be directly soldered to lead out the antenna?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1053
#: b5664e877cf74b5297439cc5d188c267
msgid "可以焊接，因为座子和天线引脚是导通的"
msgstr ""
"Yes. It can be soldered, because the socket and the antenna pin are "
"connected."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1056
#: 4bbeca2d5bb047f99680a5433b861c1d
msgid "有对讲机的模块吗"
msgstr "Do you have modules for walkie-talkies?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1057
#: 0ec87e8716dd4c0db60eb4bba10d85ae
msgid "可以推荐使用2.4G或者lora模块"
msgstr "2.4G or LoRa modules can be recommended."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1060
#: c6501c1014b6419ca9d5696b4bd64232
msgid "Lora模块同频情况下如何防止相互干扰"
msgstr ""
"How can mutual interference be prevented when LoRa modules operate at the "
"same frequency?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1061
#: 02c9ea9f30d64391b848821258f2e373
msgid "同频会产生干扰，需要自己做协议筛选信息"
msgstr ""
"Same-frequency operation causes interference. You need to implement protocol-"
"level message filtering yourself."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1064
#: b69eefd041454282b05c86705e42c98a
msgid "Ra-08模组与RG-02网关在470M频段通信需要注意什么"
msgstr ""
"What should be noted when the Ra-08 module communicates with the RG-02 "
"gateway in the 470M band?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1065
#: 94dc1f43b2bf4fbc95f519ab59f62fb3
msgid "CRXP指令参数设置505300000，频点掩码需要设置0400"
msgstr ""
"The CRXP command parameter should be set to 505300000, and the frequency "
"mask should be set to 0400."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1068
#: 5e6816e8438e4279b85e2018edd14822
msgid "Ra-08模组如果不需要dataDown数据上传该如何做"
msgstr "What should be done if the Ra-08 module does not need dataDown uplink?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1069
#: 6cc6371c397a40989d68752604f1f3e4
msgid "AT+DTRX指令上需要将confirm禁掉"
msgstr "Disable confirm in the AT+DTRX command."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1072
#: 4979b0171a624acab62678b5eadf518f
msgid ""
"请问一下我用STM32驱动Ra-01模组的时候，debug的情况下可以正常启动模组读取数据，"
"可是直接运行起来又出问题，是什么原因呢？"
msgstr ""
"When I use STM32 to drive the Ra-01 module, the module can start normally "
"and read data during debugging, but problems occur when it runs directly. "
"What is the reason?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1073
#: 20bd4b304e9f4e56a682c7fd88b28262
msgid ""
"debug模式下，为单步运行，时序可控，因此要检查程序中指令与指令之间是否有时隙。"
"排查指令发送之间冲突原因。"
msgstr ""
"In debug mode, the program runs step by step and timing is controllable. "
"Therefore, check whether there are sufficient time gaps between commands in "
"the program. Troubleshoot command timing conflicts."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1076
#: 45b1ebf8e0f44064b456e28b3b6f9c0c
msgid "请问一下，RG-02网关可以通过4G与私有服务器通过MQTT通讯么？"
msgstr ""
"Can the RG-02 gateway communicate with a private server through MQTT over 4G?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1077
#: d9ee5298df84402c9f99e7c495dfaaa2
msgid ""
"可以的，请参考说明文档。 https://blog.csdn.net/Boantong_/article/"
"details/126717812?spm=1001.2014.3001.5501"
msgstr ""
"Yes. Please refer to the documentation. https://blog.csdn.net/Boantong_/"
"article/details/126717812?spm=1001.2014.3001.5501"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1081
#: 5a86fad6af6441a1a1681f96b33773f3
msgid "请问一下Ra-01S模组的晶振有温度补偿功能么？"
msgstr ""
"Does the Ra-01S module crystal oscillator have temperature compensation?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1082
#: 186f22c6417a422bafa1fbbb4168e511
msgid "该模组用的普通晶振，没有温度补偿功能；"
msgstr ""
"This module uses an ordinary crystal oscillator and does not have "
"temperature compensation."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1085
#: 2ab172846a074d22b39ddf06aa396b3a
msgid "请问一下1276芯片不是全频段的么，为何Ra-01H模组频段为800多到900多兆？"
msgstr ""
"Since the 1276 chip is full-band, why is the Ra-01H module frequency band "
"limited to the 800–900MHz range?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1086
#: dc8f6941b0dd4176b4ea4e817bf377a7
msgid ""
"模组中的射频电路专门做了射频区间的，该芯片也可以设置其他频率，但是信号会很"
"差；"
msgstr ""
"The RF circuit in the module is specifically designed for a certain RF "
"range. The chip can be configured to other frequencies, but the signal will "
"be poor."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1089
#: cc8071d1c7c84067896fa4ab21f9c333
msgid "请问Ra-01模组分主从的吗？"
msgstr "Does the Ra-01 module distinguish between master and slave?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1090
#: 90ada8ba83db43e7b59a31aa80849f39
msgid ""
"该模组为纯射频模块，仅实现数据透传，需MCU驱动，主从功能是应用层面的，需用户开"
"发实现；我们提供驱动demo，请查看链接：https://docs.ai-thinker.com/%E5%BC"
"%80%E5%8F%91%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99"
msgstr ""
"This module is a pure RF module and only implements data transparent "
"transmission. It needs to be driven by an MCU. Master/slave functionality is "
"at the application layer and needs to be developed by the user. We provide "
"driver demos. Please refer to: https://docs.ai-thinker.com/%E5%BC%80%E5%8F"
"%91%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1093
#: 66eb7ef800cd486ea1ba972b5a44ab96
msgid "请问Ra-08H模组设置工作频点为923MHz可以么？"
msgstr "Can the Ra-08H module be set to operate at 923MHz?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1097
#: eff69ecdaaeb477b95420bb1aeb6a2ca
msgid "请问Ra-08-Kit有EU433固件么？"
msgstr "Does the Ra-08-Kit have EU433 firmware?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1098
#: 2a67bca1cbb0436b9cd6c52dd0660c3d
msgid "当前没有该固件"
msgstr "There is currently no such firmware."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1101
#: 6f4b06907615441da36e65fce126969e
msgid "RA-01模块能用在打窝船主板上吗"
msgstr "Can the RA-01 module be used on a bait boat mainboard?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1102
#: 7b619eca02ed4331a23969345df00168
msgid "可以使用"
msgstr "Yes."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1105
#: e3ec8079831947fb8c72e4741074a04f
msgid "Lora模块在CAD模式中，SF及BW的参数正常设置多少比较合适"
msgstr "In LoRa CAD mode, what are suitable normal settings for SF and BW?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1106
#: 29ae4171fd8b40c4b1d3886d01933743
msgid "根据测试环境进行调整，以实测为准"
msgstr ""
"Adjust according to the test environment, and use actual test results as the "
"standard."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1109
#: f128265f347046929906cef979b27fd8
msgid "Lora接收模式空闲状态和接收超时的区别是什么？"
msgstr ""
"What is the difference between idle state and receive timeout in LoRa "
"receive mode?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1110
#: 07baeb6fcf9b49acbba4ebddee17ee28
msgid ""
"空闲状态指的是模块没有接收到发送方的数据，接收超时指的是模块在指定时间内没有"
"接收到发送方的数据"
msgstr ""
"Idle state means the module has not received data from the sender. Receive "
"timeout means the module did not receive data from the sender within the "
"specified time."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1113
#: 074a17afa19c4873aede98deeb46e1a1
msgid "Ra-01SC可以用在arduino和ESP32上吗"
msgstr "Can Ra-01SC be used with Arduino and ESP32?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1114
#: bc3cb182b65c44069760693d7cea05a4
msgid "模组可以使用，有对应的arduino示例"
msgstr ""
"The module can be used, and corresponding Arduino examples are available."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1117
#: 29db286c240142c4b3a47cb7c5bea200
msgid "Ra-08支持片上开发吗"
msgstr "Does Ra-08 support on-chip development?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1118
#: d00f29bc296045068f183fecba2634a5
msgid "模组支持开发，有对应的SDK和教程"
msgstr ""
"The module supports development, and corresponding SDKs and tutorials are "
"available."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1121
#: a1e086f23d244e1880e75beba1376a20
msgid "Lora测试板可以连接电脑吗"
msgstr "Can the LoRa test board be connected to a computer?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1122
#: d1e4af6a8e7442d8ab53481238f88aad
msgid "可以，不过需要配合串口板去连接"
msgstr "Yes, but it needs to be connected through a serial port board."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1125
#: d3b65703a0294170ae71874f8e294f86
msgid "Ra-08可以用pathy吗"
msgstr "Can Ra-08 use pathy?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1126
#: 7b0a3736ee824810a532d1c540aef8d6
msgid "不可以使用"
msgstr "No."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1129
#: d5a7eb09cbb846e395b97b9acfcec21d
msgid "有没有支持测距的lora模块"
msgstr "Are there any LoRa modules that support ranging?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1130
#: e39a0e28d99c4c55ac68d5b5ab133049
msgid "目前没有，如需测距可以选择UWB模块"
msgstr "Not currently. If ranging is required, a UWB module can be selected."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1133
#: 04894073bd624ba3a5e0c14ee5cf23b3
msgid "Lora模块可以支持MQTT吗"
msgstr "Can LoRa modules support MQTT?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1134
#: 5b819b33aa9f4ebaa97070f813167aea
msgid "不可以，如需使用MQTT必须要接一个WIFI模块实现"
msgstr "No. To use MQTT, a Wi-Fi module must be connected."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1137
#: 75316600672b48899d238f0649caf0e4
msgid ""
"请问433M天线跟470M天线用起来一样的么？对信号是否有影响，目前用的470M频段，买"
