msgstr "It can be used, and the signal impact is not significant."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1141
#: 61db739a536e4c8abf357e70387a5729
msgid "请问是否有发射功率大于22db的lora模块？"
msgstr "Are there any LoRa modules with transmit power greater than 22dB?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1142
#: 83d994db8f1244149a6308bbcc77bb3f
msgid "没有"
msgstr "No."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1145
#: 8f1268a37c204f93bdd5b21eacc37c58
msgid "请问RG-02网关最多支持连接多少个设备？多了会有什么后果？"
msgstr ""
"How many devices can the RG-02 gateway support at most? What happens if "
"there are more?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1146
#: 001711783a6646aa975a2847248a1705
msgid "200个，多了会丢包严重"
msgstr "200 devices. If there are more, packet loss will become serious."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1150
#: 6725a4f4c86749218830a23bfe83a935
msgid "请问LoRa模块可以用51单片机驱动么？"
msgstr "Can LoRa modules be driven by a 51 MCU?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1151
